{"tid":1186890,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗性侵案完結！女方已自願撤銷控訴","createTime":"2019-06-05T08:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T06:00:34.000Z","uid":1426,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ade5568dc8d157c40b763da54227074ab0b712ce","tid":1186890,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T08:53:00.000Z","msg":"　C.朗拿度（C.Ronaldo）性侵案曾鬧的沸沸揚揚，這也讓C.朗拿度陷入了不小的麻煩之中。現如今此事終於畫上了句號，女方撤銷了對C.朗拿度的指控。<br />\n<br />\n　　彭博社透露，C.朗拿度性侵案女主馬祖爾已經在上個月向美國內華達州法國提交了自願撤訴的通知，這意味著C.朗拿度終於從這樁風波中抽身。不過彭博社同時表示，尚不清楚C.朗拿度是否和馬祖爾在庭外達成了和解。<br />\n<br />\n　　2009年，C.朗拿度在美國拉斯維加斯和馬祖爾發生了性關係，之後女方指控C.朗拿度強姦，但雙方曾在當時達成過和解協議，C.朗拿度給馬祖爾支付了37萬美元封口費。不過在去年，馬祖爾卻再次指控C.朗拿度強姦。在馬祖爾指控之後，美國警方對這樁案件開啟調查。<br />\n<br />\n　　過去一個賽季裡，C.朗拿度力助祖記奪得了意甲冠軍。接下來C.朗拿度的重點將是國家隊比賽，他將隨葡萄牙隊出戰歐國聯4強。在大戰之前C.朗拿度去掉了身上的麻煩，這無疑對於他來說是個好消息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Asmssa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Asmssa.gif&h=f724d09f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ihopqdR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FihopqdR.gif&h=e1f427f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMU0H0y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMU0H0y.gif&h=1e05e37d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb43f8b2dd1ed43152b9ca4d5c4ca60cc7cc7929","tid":1186890,"uid":131369,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"王騎又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67c21c1f0e262493cae29995168a7a0171f3a5f","tid":1186890,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb43f8b2dd1ed43152b9ca4d5c4ca60cc7cc7929","tid":1186890,"uid":131369,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"王騎又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />